​11 Labs Text to Audio Generator is a powerful tool designed to convert text into high-quality, natural-sounding speech using ElevenLabs' advanced AI technology. This extension provides a seamless mobile experience, allowing you to generate, play, and manage audio files directly within your environment. With built-in features like token tracking, custom playback controls, and easy sharing, it offers an efficient workflow for content creators. Optimized for accessibility and performance, this tool makes AI-powered voice generation simple and fast.